{"tid":1476086,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)詭屋驚凶實錄/厲陰宅 反斗奇兵外傳 哥師奶大亂鬥","createTime":"2019-08-15T16:37:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T22:04:51.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"57c8eb5e5d1c426d9c60aabe915994a48d71a6f1","tid":1476086,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:37:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=veK8Cd5y3rx0%2F3TK36JPEilZyh30VB0jKt3ffwT98zY%3D&h=3e7c04d1\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=veK8Cd5y3rx0%2F3TK36JPEilZyh30VB0jKt3ffwT98zY%3D&h=a8434948\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=veK8Cd5y3rx0%2F3TK36JPEilZyh30VB0jKt3ffwT98zY%3D&h=c57852d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/1/1f/Conjuring_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F1%2F1f%2FConjuring_poster.jpg&h=e4680cdf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/0/06/Annabelle_doll.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F0%2F06%2FAnnabelle_doll.jpg&h=bb3313e4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://driver.cool3c.com/files/3/a38e8b96-b78a-4242-b365-59dc3cd4874c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdriver.cool3c.com%2Ffiles%2F3%2Fa38e8b96-b78a-4242-b365-59dc3cd4874c.jpg&h=d56f0f72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.1971年，美國羅德島州哈維爾，羅傑和卡洛琳&middot;佩倫帶著五個女兒安卓莉亞、南希、克莉絲汀、辛蒂和愛普，搬進一棟郊區大宅，但屋內幾天下來開始發生一連串超自然現象：一家的寵物狗在搬進去的第二天就神秘死亡，家中所有鐘全部停在淩晨三點零七分，房子瀰漫著一股腐爛屍臭，而一樓的門會自行頻繁開了又關，卡洛琳的身上頻繁會出現不該存在的淤青、克莉絲汀睡覺時老是覺得有人在抓她的腳、有夢遊症的辛蒂睡著時會用頭不停地撞擊一個老櫥櫃、而愛普不停地在跟一個「想像朋友」羅伊說話。幾天的晚上，卡洛琳跟著一段拍手聲走進堆滿老舊物品的地下室，卻被反鎖在裡面，點上一根火柴照光後卻在腦後注意到一雙拍手手掌。而在二樓，安卓莉亞與辛蒂也遭到過一個不明惡靈的攻擊，惡靈自行消失後，一家人才確信這些現象絕非尋常<br />\n<br />\n2.驅魔師夫婦艾德和蘿琳受到委託，指安娜貝爾內藏一個凶惡的邪靈，為避免安娜貝爾造成更多破壞，夫婦將這個安娜貝爾玩偶帶回了他們家中，並帶進「詛咒物房間」，將她安置於聖三一教堂拆遷遺下的玻璃所製造的玻璃櫃里，並且附上神父的祝福。<br />\n然而，前去參加茱蒂生日派對的丹妮拉對鎖上了的「詛咒物房間」感到好奇，並在艾德的房間里找到了鑰匙，而且誤打誤撞地把封印著安娜貝爾的櫃子打開了<br />\n<br />\n3.時間來到五年後，期間馬克過著酗酒的荒廢生活，與艾瑪離婚並且離開君主組織，而艾瑪則是帶著麥蒂森，母女倆繼續在君主組織的中國雲南61號基地裡研究摩斯拉的卵。這一天，卵突然孵化，幼蟲型態的怪獸：摩斯拉從裡頭竄出，雖然使出封鎖裝置但疑似遭人破壞，感受到威脅而激動的摩斯拉開始攻擊研究人員，艾瑪不得不使用自己剛完成的裝置&quot;奧卡&quot;，奧卡能針對巨獸而發出各種頻率以控制行動並成功使摩斯拉平靜下來，但基地卻在此時爆炸遭人入侵，由喬納．艾倫領導的生態恐怖分子組織攻擊並綁架走艾瑪和麥蒂森，而後摩斯拉逃脫並在附近的瀑布結繭<br />\n<br />\n12 45AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=veK8Cd5y3rx0%2F3TK36JPEilZyh30VB0jKt3ffwT98zY%3D&h=dbad49dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=veK8Cd5y3rx0%2F3TK36JPEilZyh30VB0jKt3ffwT98zY%3D&h=6d943360\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eb7ae421460555a232e8b1b674ae69cdb8bcb38","tid":1476086,"uid":79046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:38:18.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n行過路過入嚟望下，千載難逢嘅機會啊！８２３和理非<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">人鏈</span></span></strong>，萬人齊築香江路！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［和理非升級］一生人一次嘅機會嚟喇！！！！想唔想上Buzzfeed 9GAG？！？！？！？！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475842\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475842</a>"},{"pid":"ead1b28e6b6fa31ef61f5b2ba5a70615cc83aab5","tid":1476086,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T17:05:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b6f75f62b5322e042e1155dd1c744d9fb323f87","tid":1476086,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T17:52:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93027555565d924532246c680443a793b581d3b1","tid":1476086,"uid":291601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T17:57:33.000Z","msg":"好意思，借個位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">816全民㩒錢日，藍絲一齊撐</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1476207\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1476207</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"84ed60389eb940f2c8f4c00c681b5b698d2028e